\section desc Description
<!-- Short description of what this package is supposed to provide -->

This package is part of the Simulation Validation Suite. It produces histograms for validating Tracks.


\subsection interface Public interface
<!-- List the classes that are provided for use in other packages (if any) -->

- MultiTrackValidator
- RecoTrackSelector
- SiPixelTrackingRecHitsValid
- SiStripTrackingRecHitsValid
- TPEfficiencySelector
- TPFakeRateSelector
- TrackEfficiencySelector
- TrackFakeRateSelector

\subsection modules Modules
<!-- Describe modules implemented in this package and their parameter set -->

- MultiTrackValidator: module for Track Validation
- SiStripTrackingRecHitsValid: module for validation of Strip Hits used for tracking
- SiPixelTrackingRecHitsValid: module for validation of Pixel Hits used for tracking
-  TrackSelector: selector for reco::Tracks
-  TrackSelectorForEfficiency: deprecated 
-  TrackSelectorForFakeRate: deprecated 
-  TPSelectorForEfficiency: selector of TrackingParticles for efficiency studies
-  TPSelectorForFakeRate: selector of TrackingParticles for fake rate studies

